pageProduct.name: Thompson's Natural Liquid Calcium 60 Capsules New Formula
pageProduct.description:
Information


General Information

Thompson's Natural Liquid Calcium supports healthy bones and teeth.

Vitamin D helps with calcium absorption, and Vitamin D deficiency is considered a world-wide health concern. Thompson's Natural Liquid Calcium combines calcium with vitamin D3 for:
- Assisting healthy bone growth and development. 
- Helping support bone mineralisation & bone health. 
- Maintaining healthy teeth and supporting teeth mineralisation.

A diet deficient in calcium can lead to osteoporosis in later life. Calcium may help preven1 osteoporosis when dietary intake is inadequate. Women's calcium requirements are also increased after menopause.

Size: 60 Capsules

KEY FEATURES

• Assist healthy bone growth and development.
• Helps support bone mineralisation & bone health
• Maintain healthy teeth and supporting teeth mineralisation.
• Calcium source

Warnings

If symptoms persist, talk to your heath professional.
Do not use if bottle and/or cap seal is missing or broken.

CAUTION

Keep out of reach of children.

PRECAUTIONS

Vitamin supplements should not replace a balanced diet.

Ingredients

Active Ingredients: Active Ingredient per capsule:
Calcium Carbonate 907mg
equiv. to Calcium 350mg
Colecalciferol 8.3mcg
equiv. to Vitamin D3 333IU

Contains: Soya bean products.

Allergen Contains: Soybean

Allergen Free From: Artificial Flavours| Dairy| Egg| Fish| Gluten| Lactose| Nuts| Sesame Seeds| Sugar

Directions

Store below 30°C in a dry place.

Storage Temperature: Below 30°C

RECYCLABLE INFORMATION

Remove cap and recycle glass.

Recyclable Packaging?: Yes
